    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05e6",
      "text": "code:hatena",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05e7",
      "text": " <body>",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05e8",
      "text": " *1239338527*カードゲーム作り",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05e9",
      "text": " f:id:nishiohirokazu:20090410134207j:image",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05ea",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05eb",
      "text": " プラバンを買ってきて矢印チップを2枚作った。片方がプログラムカウンタで片方がジャンプ先ラベル。カードは単語カードに手書き18枚。あとは5色20枚入りのポーカーチップを買って、これで2色を+/-トークンとして使って3人まで対戦可能。ゲームルール的には何人でもプレイできるけどあんまり人数が多くても制御不能になる上に一周の時間がかかるようになって面白くないので、まあ2人対戦がメイン、たまに3～4人でやってもいいかも、という感じを想定している。",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05ec",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05ed",
      "text": " だいぶ形になってきた。面白い。次はカードを手書きじゃなくするか。",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05ee",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05ef",
      "text": " *1239340275*[SpaMon]多人数プレイの考察",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f0",
      "text": " プレイヤーがやたらとたくさんいておのおの2ビットを置くときにどこにおくのが有利か。",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f1",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f2",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f3",
      "text": " 2ビットの方がゲーム性が豊かだと思うけどまずは1ビットで考えるか。Bomb, Charmは発動すると自分が死ぬので置けない。JumpとReverseでは自分が勝利できないのでこれもダメ。MoveCardもダメ。ダントツに使えるカードはMakeBitだが、みんながここに積んできた場合逆に後手がRemoveCardにつんで削除しにくるという手が危険。4人が結託してSurgeに置けば置いていない人を倒せる。あとはMakeBitをコピーできるカードやRemoveCardをコピーしてRemoveCard自体を削除できるカードが危険か。",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f4",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f5",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f6",
      "text": " 次に2ビットのときを考える。MakeBitに積むのはいいとして、MakeBit派はMakeBitに早くPCを持ってきたい。逆にSurge派は先にSurgeに持ってきたい。MakeBitでビットを増やしてもSurgeを4発当てられたら負ける。一方MakeBitで好きなところにビットを増やしてSurgeにPCが渡らないようにコントロールできる可能性も高い。2枚目のビットではお互い相手の陣営の足をどうやれば引っ張れるかという戦いになり、長期戦はSurgeが不利。",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f7",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f8",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05f9",
      "text": " ふむ。2人対戦のときでも先手、後手、後手、先手の順に2つだけ置くルールでも割と楽しめるかもしれない。",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05fa",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05fb",
      "text": " *1239342704*Vコンビネータの導出",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05fc",
      "text": " 昨日はベッドの上で昼間わからなかった Vx = V の導出を考えていたらわかった",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05fd",
      "text": " Ax = xとなるxはM(BAM)であることが割と簡単に証明できる。M(BAM) = (BAM)(BAM) = A(M(BAM))。Kx = xたるxはVであることは簡単に示せる。Kxy = x, Kxy = (Kx)y = xy. thus xy = x. で、あとはM = SIIとI = SKKまでは理解していたのでBをSから導出するだけ。",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05fe",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d05ff",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0600",
      "text": " Sってとても便利で、いらない引数をくくりだすことができる。",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0601",
      "text": " >||",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0602",
      "text": " 1: xX = (I x)(KX x) = SI(KX)x",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0603",
      "text": " 2: X(Yx) = (KX x)(Y x) = S(KX)Yx",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0604",
      "text": " 3: XxY = (X x)(KY x) = SX(KY)x",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0605",
      "text": " 4: Xx(Yx) = (X x)(Y x) = SXYx",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0606",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0607",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0608",
      "text": " >||",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0609",
      "text": " Bxyz = x(yz)",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d060a",
      "text": " = (Kx z)(y z)",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d060b",
      "text": " = S(Kx)yz",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d060c",
      "text": " = (KS x)(K x) yz",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d060d",
      "text": " = S(KS)K xyz",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d060e",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d060f",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0610",
      "text": " よって",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0611",
      "text": " >||",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0612",
      "text": " V = M(BKM)",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0613",
      "text": " = ( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) )( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) )",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0614",
      "text": " Vx = ( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) )( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) )x",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0615",
      "text": " = ( (KS)K (KK)(S(SKK)(SKK)) )...",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0616",
      "text": " = S (KK) (S(SKK)(SKK))  ( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) )x",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0617",
      "text": " = (KK)(...) ( (S(SKK)(SKK))  ( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) )) x",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0618",
      "text": " = K ( (S(SKK)(SKK))  ( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) )) x",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0619",
      "text": " = (S(SKK)(SKK))  ( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) ) # xが消えた！",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d061a",
      "text": " = (SKK)( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) ) ((SKK)( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) ))",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d061b",
      "text": " = K( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) ) (...) K( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) ) (...)",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d061c",
      "text": " = ( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) )( (S(KS)KK) (S(SKK)(SKK)) ) # 元の形に戻った！",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d061d",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d061e",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d061f",
      "text": " この感動を伝えきれていない自信がとてもある。",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec22aff09e00003d0620",
      "text": " </body>",
      "created": 1239289200,
      "updated": 1239289200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
